{"tid":1563522,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"究極殘股鳩坐等冚球爆","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T01:58:00.000Z","uid":125976,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d61295eb26b7c51fc90cf62e5d841119efe61c23","tid":1563522,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"有人話冚球爆之前會有個最大嘅泡沫大升浪，就同你賭吓𠵱個浪上唔上到去，因為冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近睇晒啲數據，其實而家好似 06 - 07 年，債息開始倒掛，全球開始減息，股市亦會變得更加泡沫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時嚟講最殘都應該係港股，因為貿易戰關係升唔起，所以喺𠵱個市場搵啲殘中之殘嘅股唔太難，但會唔會大升真係唔知，但至少好難跌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟小試牛刀，試吓搵啲極殘股出嚟鳩坐，坐到個市爆為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">免責聲明：\n投資殘股涉及風險，價格可升可跌，甚至變成毫無價值。巴打絲打於作出任何投資或決定前，或可諮詢獨立專業顧問意見。</code></pre>"},{"pid":"eb10c20c6ff5ddf6bc3f91e618b7a5f37e84d2c4","tid":1563522,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e0bc44830b067dc16d71a6d9017ddaca38d383f5","tid":1563522,"uid":4801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci